The paper proposes a reinforcement learning algorithm for optimizing antenna tilt angle and beamwidths in a heterogeneous cellular network. This involves learning user locations and adapting to environmental changes in the network. The paper utilizes deep neural networks and multi-agent mean field RL algorithms. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
